videos.headline: Maurer's mom loves his first career pass for Vols TD
videos.description: Brian Maurer's mother approves of her son's first college completion that goes to Marquez Callaway for a 73-yard Tennessee touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Maurer's mom loves his 1st career pass for Vols TD) 2019/10/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vols QB Maurer strikes again with 2nd TD pass
videos.description: Brian Maurer zips a pass over the middle to Jauan Jennings for a 12-yard Tennessee touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Vols QB Maurer strikes again with 2nd TD pass) 2019/10/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Fromm whips red-zone TD to Cager
videos.description: Georgia cashes in its red-zone opportunity on Jake Fromm's touchdown strike to Lawrence Cager.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Fromm whips red-zone TD to Cager) 2019/10/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Maurer gets absolutely blasted, Georgia recovers for TD
videos.description: Georgia DB Eric Stokes lights up Brian Maurer, who loses the ball and it is recovered by Geo Tae Crowder for a 60-yard defensive touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Maurer gets absolutely blasted, Georgia recovers for TD) 2019/10/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Georgia stays undefeated with balanced win vs. Tennessee
videos.description: Georgia scores two touchdowns through the air, two on the ground and one on defense as the Bulldogs down the Volunteers to remain unbeaten.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Georgia stays undefeated with balanced win vs. Tennessee) 2019/10/5 ESHEET SOTFULL
